Backend components:
1. `User` entity (users table: id, email unique, password_hash, role, created_at)
2. `UserRepository`
3. `auth/AuthService` — register, login
4. `auth/JwtService` — issue/parse JWT (jjwt 0.12.6)
5. `auth/AuthInterceptor` (HandlerInterceptor) — parse Bearer token, set auth context; role checks
